❤️❤️❤️❤️ Welcome back @makegirlz to Instagram! The account was hacked and we spent the past couple of days retrieving it and yesterday we got it back up and running for all of you beauty lovers 🙏❤️❤️ Thank you to everyone who helped out, and a special thanks to all of my Bay Area friends and the @mayabeautestudios team who helped out! On another note we have been prepping for amazing new content so stay tuned, excuse the lack of posts but we are back too 😘❤️❤️ هلا ب @makegirlz نورت الانستاغرام!!! الحساب تهكر و مضينا الأيام الماضية عّم نشتغل لنرجعه و اخيراً رجعناه الحمدالله، شكر كبير لكل اصدقاءي اللي ساعدونا، والله ما قصرتو مشكورين كتير ❤️❤️❤️ #mayabeaute #makegirlz
